{"tid":166030,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新貓適應","createTime":"2017-03-21T19:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T18:38:14.000Z","uid":10170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0229cb3b0b6ee954080ca20f40940669938506","tid":166030,"uid":10170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T19:23:11.000Z","msg":"如果新貓唻到屋企，本身已經養緊一隻（舊貓細過新貓）點樣可以令佢地關係變好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔同種係咪冇影響？"},{"pid":"f8090450b44b06dd71c0bb5c7dc574436ac4d7cd","tid":166030,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T19:24:55.000Z","msg":"唔養"},{"pid":"ba386e03ba80008eaa7fecb7400a6c272bf3445c","tid":166030,"uid":84759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果新貓唻到屋企，本身已經養緊一隻（舊貓細過新貓）點樣可以令佢地關係變好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔同種係咪冇影響？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最好係雙方頭幾次接觸等佢地聞下對方氣味先，之後再面對面見對方，咁樣唔會令佢地覺得太突然。<br />\n但我自己無咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後都係放佢地係屋企，佢地自己慢慢就變到關係好好。<br />\n<br />\n我養既都係唔同種，無咩關係同影響"},{"pid":"f70961463ce72381dda05865bc19b0295b9b3af8","tid":166030,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"親嚟嗰隻一定要困籠<br />\n除非兩隻貓性格都係friendly"},{"pid":"66956a03877add96f8d4ace1a330dfa7f5f82656","tid":166030,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"新貓困籠養七日左右已經有效果"},{"pid":"28246a74eb9a09ef82f1e6ac95f685ee1813db1d","tid":166030,"uid":10170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T18:38:14.000Z","msg":"初初唻頭一兩日係新貓fee舊貓 <br />\n但自從舊貓瀨左屎之後就開始fee返籠入面隻新貓<br />\n<br />\n依家好似第6/7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}